'From Squeak3.1alpha of 5 February 2001 [latest update: #4201] on 16 July 2001 at 2:07:22 pm'!"Change Set:		navNewbuttonDate:			16 July 2001Author:			Bob ArningAdd a 'new project' button to the standard navigator"!!ProjectNavigationMorph methodsFor: 'as yet unclassified' stamp: 'RAA 7/16/2001 14:06'!currentNavigatorVersion	^23		"since these guys get saved, we fix them up if they are older versions"! !!ProjectNavigationMorph methodsFor: 'as yet unclassified' stamp: 'RAA 7/16/2001 14:06'!makeTheButtons	^{		self buttonShare.		self buttonPrev.		self buttonNext.		self buttonPublish.		self buttonNewer.		self buttonTell.		self buttonFind.		self buttonFullScreen.		self buttonFlaps.		self buttonPaint.		self buttonUndo.		self buttonNewProject.	}! !!ProjectNavigationMorph methodsFor: 'the buttons' stamp: 'RAA 7/16/2001 14:06'!buttonNewProject	^self makeButton: 'NEW' balloonText: 'Start a new project' for: #newProject! !